src:
Bivši kapiten Partizana je slobodan igrač
06 Nov 2019, 16:54 by Milos
Kratko je trajala misija Milenka Tepića u redovima italijanskog Varezea.
„Sportando“ javlja, da je nekadašnji reprezentativac naše zemlje raskinuo saradnju sa klubom za koji je odigrao samo tri utakmice u Seriji A i prosečno beležio jedan poen po meču.
Tepić ima 32 godine, a tokom karijere igrao je za Vojvodinu, Partizan, Panatinaikos, Sevilju, Ritas, PAOK, Orlandinu i Brindizi.

POVEZANE OBJAVE
text:
The former Partizan captain is a free agent
06 Nov 2019, 15:54 by Milos
The mission of Milenko Tepic in the Italian Varese ran briefly.
Sportando reports that a former national team player has broken off his partnership with a club for which he played only three Serie A games and averaged one point per match.
Tepic is 32 years old and has played for Vojvodina, Partizan, Panathinaikos, Seville, Ritas, PAOK, Orlandina and Brindisi throughout his career.
